---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How much does an automated gate cost in Pakenham?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "In 2026, a custom pedestrian gate across Cardinia typically runs about $400–$1,200 supplied and installed, a manual driveway gate roughly $1,500–$4,000 depending on size and material, and full automation adds about $1,800–$4,500 for the motor, controls and wiring. A worked example: a 4-metre sliding Colorbond driveway gate at $3,200 with a $2,600 slider motor and remotes comes to around $5,800." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Sliding or swing gate for my driveway?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Sliding gates suit narrow frontages and sloping driveways common around Cardinia Lakes and Officer because they do not swing into the drive. Swing gates suit wider, flatter entrances and give a more traditional look. We assess your slope, width and the way you drive in before recommending one." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can you automate an existing gate?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Often, yes — if the existing gate is sound and properly hung we can fit a slider or swing-arm motor, safety sensors, remotes and a keypad or intercom to it. If the gate is sagging or under-built we'll tell you, because automation only works reliably on a gate that is hung true." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you match gates to my fence?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. We build gates to match your boundary — Colorbond to a Colorbond fence, timber to a timber fence, or aluminium and tubular for a feature entrance. Matching the gate to the run is what makes the whole frontage look finished rather than patched together." }
    }
  ]
};
---
<Layout
  title="Gates & Automation Pakenham | Driveway & Pedestrian Gates | Pakenham Fencing"
  description="Custom gates & automation in Pakenham & Cardinia — sliding & swing driveway gates, pedestrian gates, motors & remotes to match your fence. (03) 9003 0108."
  canonical="https://pakenhamfencingco.com.au/services/gates-automation/">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  </Fragment>

  <section class="hero hero-suburb">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Gates &amp; Automation</span>
      <h1>Gates &amp; automation in <span class="accent">Pakenham</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Custom pedestrian and driveway gates &mdash; sliding and swing &mdash; built
        to match your fence and fitted with reliable automation. Tidy, secure
        entrances for homes across Pakenham and the Cardinia growth corridor.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>The gate finishes the fence.</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 60rem;">
        <p>
          A boundary is only as good as the way you get in and out of it. We build
          custom pedestrian and driveway gates to match the fence &mdash; whether we
          installed it or not &mdash; so the whole frontage reads as one job.
          Colorbond gates to a Colorbond run, timber to timber, or a tubular and
          aluminium feature gate where you want the entrance to stand out. Across the
          newer estates of Cardinia Lakes, Officer and Heritage Springs a clean
          automated gate is fast becoming the expected finish.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sliding or swing depends on your block. Sliding gates suit narrow frontages
          and the sloping driveways that are common across the corridor, because they
          track sideways instead of swinging into the drive. Swing gates suit wider,
          flatter entrances and give a more traditional look. We weld and hang every
          gate true, because a gate that is not hung properly will sag, bind and
          wreck any motor fitted to it.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Automation that keeps working.</h3>
        <p>
          We fit slider and swing-arm motors with safety sensors, remotes, keypads
          and intercom options to suit how you live. On rural and acreage entrances
          around Pakenham Upper and Gembrook, where the wind and the distances are
          bigger, we spec heavier-duty motors and braced gate frames so the gate
          keeps cycling reliably for years. All electrical work is done to AS/NZS
          3000.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">What it costs.</h3>
        <p>
          As a 2026 guide: a custom pedestrian gate runs about $400&ndash;$1,200, a
          manual driveway gate roughly $1,500&ndash;$4,000, and automation adds about
          $1,800&ndash;$4,500 for the motor, controls and wiring. A worked example: a
          4-metre sliding Colorbond driveway gate at $3,200 with a $2,600 slider motor
          and remotes is around $5,800, supplied and installed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Related fencing &amp; areas.</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 60rem;">
        <p>
          Building the fence at the same time? Pair your gate with
          <a href="/services/colorbond-fencing/">Colorbond fencing</a> or
          <a href="/services/timber-paling-fencing/">timber paling fencing</a> for a
          matched frontage. We fit gates and automation across
          <a href="/officer/">Officer</a> and
          <a href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a> &mdash; and the wider
          <a href="/cardinia-shire/">Cardinia Shire</a> area.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/lakeside/">Lakeside</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/heritage-springs/">Heritage Springs</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/officer/">Officer</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/cardinia-shire/">All Cardinia Shire</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Get your gate &amp; automation quote.</h2>
        <p>Tell us your driveway width and the look you want and we&rsquo;ll send a clear written price.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
